	<div class="unit-reflection">
	In the demonstrated artifact, I did an analysis with my group member on rhetorical situations and features of the response paper genre. In this analysis, I point out the purpose of the response paper genre —— expressing and sharing the author’s own opinions on a certain existing paper, and I also specify the audience and context based on my definition of the purpose. This activity is essential for successfully writing my response paper. As someone who doesn't have a lot of previous experience with this genre, having clear ideas upon this genre’s rhetorical situation and features help me understand how and why other genre conventions, like tones and mechanics, are formed. 
